  <steps>
    <step num="0">Preheat oven to 400˚F (200˚C). </step>
    <step num="1">Place chicken breast in a baking dish. Season chicken with salt and pepper, to taste. </step>
    <step num="2">Spread pesto on each chicken breast. </step>
    <step num="3">Layer tomatoes on top of the chicken. </step>
    <step num="4">Top with mozzarella cheese. </step>
    <step num="5">Bake for 40 minutes. </step>
    <step num="6">Enjoy! </step>
